    <h2>Roadmap to Start Trading</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Start with Equity Trading</li>
      <li>Capital should be minimum 10k and maximum 20k</li>
      <li>Use 30-50%of your capital on every trade</li>
      <li>Risk Reward ration should be minimum 1:2</li>
      <li>Wait for Profit or Stoploss-whichever is 1st</li>
      <li>Respect your Stop Loss</li>
